import { Container, Grid, Header, Segment, Statistic } from 'semantic-ui-react';
import './App.css';

function App() {
  return (

      <Container>
        <Header as='h1'>Budget</Header>
        <Statistic size='small'>
        <Statistic.Label>Your Balance:</Statistic.Label>
        <Statistic.Value>2,550.53</Statistic.Value>
        </Statistic>
        <Segment textAlign='center'>
            <Grid columns={2} divided>
                <Grid.Row>
                    <Grid.Column>
                      <Statistic size='tiny' color='green'>
                        <Statistic.Label style={{texAlign:"left"}}>
                          Income:
                        </Statistic.Label>
                        <Statistic.Value>
                          1,045.50
                        </Statistic.Value>
                      </Statistic>
                    </Grid.Column>
                    <Grid.Column>
                      <Statistic size='tiny' color='red'>
                        <Statistic.Label style={{texAlign:"left"}}>
                          Expenses:
                        </Statistic.Label>
                        <Statistic.Value>
                          623.50
                        </Statistic.Value>
                      </Statistic>
                    </Grid.Column>
                </Grid.Row>
            </Grid>
        </Segment>
      </Container>

  );
}

export default App;
